'''黑胡椒蟹'''，是一道與[[辣椒蟹|辣椒蟹]]齊名的[[新加坡|新加坡]]菜色，由{{link-en|长堤海鲜楼|Long Beach Seafood Restaurant}}於1959年所創<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.longbeachseafood.com.sg/about.php |title=Long Beach Seafood Restaurant » About Us<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-11-04 |archive-date=2013-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130213112850/http://www.longbeachseafood.com.sg/about.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
== 作法 ==
將螃蟹斬塊快炒3分鐘，再加入以[[黑胡椒|黑胡椒]]、[[花雕酒|花雕酒]]、[[老抽|老抽]]、[[蠔油|蠔油]]、[[麻油|麻油]]等多種配料调製而成的酱汁[[焖|焖]]5分鐘，上碟前放入香[[葱|葱]]即可食用<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sbs.com.au/food/recipes/singapore-wok-fried-black-pepper-crab |title=Singapore wok-fried black pepper crab |access-date=2014-11-04 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112034022/https://www.sbs.com.au/food/recipes/singapore-wok-fried-black-pepper-crab |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

